headline: Outpatient & Specialty Care Stocks Q2 Highlights: DaVita (NYSE:DVA)
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how outpatient & specialty care stocks fared in Q2, starting with DaVita (NYSE:DVA).
